      "id": "35c3e52a-2720-4bd3-9708-acbff91220a8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors also attempt to improve the performance of the model by utilizing a TF-IDF representation of the text answers. The goal here is to identify words that are indicative to the student’s grade. The resultts show that proposed methodoly represents a slight improvement over the baseline models tested. ",
